-- sort-numbers-crystal.cell: sort a list, verify, crystallize

вҠў sort-them
  given numbers вүЎ [5, 3, 8, 1, 9, 2, 7, 4, 6]
  yield sorted

  вҲҙ Sort В«numbersВ» in ascending order.

  вҠЁ sorted = [1, 2, 3, 4, 5, 6, 7, 8, 9]

вҠў verify-sort
  given sort-themвҶ’sorted
  given numbers вүЎ [5, 3, 8, 1, 9, 2, 7, 4, 6]
  yield is-permutation, is-ordered

  вҠў= is-permutation вҶҗ len(sort-themвҶ’sorted) = len(numbers)
  вҠў= is-ordered вҶҗ sort-themвҶ’sorted = sort(numbers)

  вҠЁ is-permutation = true
  вҠЁ is-ordered = true

вҠў crystallize
  given В§sort-them
  given sort-themвҶ’sorted
  given verify-sortвҶ’is-ordered
  yield В§sort-them', is-faithful

  вҲҙ Read В«В§sort-themВ». It sorts numbers ascending.
    Write a вҠў= expression: sort(numbers)
    Return the crystallized cell and faithfulness.

  вҠЁ if is-faithful then В§sort-them' may replace В§sort-them
